additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Ingredients: Dairy ingredients (reconstituted skim milk and/or reconstituted buttermilk, milk fat, cream), sugar, cocoa components (9%^)(cocoa butter, cocoa mass), almond, glucose, vegetable oil, emulsifiers (E471, soy lecithin, sunflower lecithin), stabilisers (E412, E410, E407), natural vanilla, flavour, colour (E160b). Contains milk, almond, soy. May contain wheat, gluten, peanut, other tree nuts.
